        <updateDate>2023-01-17T15:36:42Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Illegal Alien NICS Alert Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the national instant criminal background check system to notify U.S. Immigration and Customs Enforcement and relevant state and local law enforcement agencies when the system indicates that a prospective firearm transferee is illegally or unlawfully in the United States.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
